            <p style="text-align: center;" data-mce-style="text-align: center;" >
                <span style="font-family: impact, chicago;" data-mce-style="font-family: impact, chicago;">
                    <strong>
                        <span style="color: rgb(32,178,170);" data-mce-style="color: #20b2aa;"> ﻿﻿
                             Welcome CITIZEN SCIENTIST
                        </span>
                    </strong>
                </span>
                <br>
            </p>
            </h2>
        </div>
 <div data-controltype="textblock">
            <p style="text-align: center;" >
                        Engage in existing Research Projects you find interesting or create your own Research Project!
            </p>
        </div>
 <div data-controltype="textblock">
            <p style="text-align: center;" >
                        All the tools you need are at your fingertips, become a Scientist and tackle questions of all sorts!
            </p>
        </div>


        <div data-controltype="textblock">

          <b>
            <p style="text-align: center;" >
              Select a Project Category
            </p>
          </b>
